data.description: Welcome Home, where potential meets opportunity in the heart of SW Atlanta! This cozy fixer-upper is a canvas waiting for a first-time homebuyer's personal touch or an investor's savvy vision. This home has 3 bedrooms/3 full baths and a BONUS ROOM!  No HOA means no extra fees, and with public transportation just a stroll away, commuting is a breeze.    This hidden gem is not just a house; it's a project with perks! Unlock its potential with the magic of an FHA 203k loan! Whether you're a first-time homebuyer with a vision or an investor ready to transform, this loan is your ticket to turning dreams into reality. Spruce up this fixer-upper and tailor it to your taste, all while financing the improvements with ease. Imagine the satisfaction of turning this space into your dream home or a lucrative investment in Atlanta's thriving real estate market.    And here's the fun twist a this charming abode is currently owner-occupied, adding that extra layer of warmth and character. If these walls could talk, they'd share tales of dreams and aspirations, ready to be passed on to the next proud owner.    Seize the chance to make this house your home or your next big venture. Contact Kizzie for a showinga after all, good things come to those who see the potential in the details! Opportunity knocks at 605 Fern Brooks Dr a answer the door and let the transformation begin. Contact us today and let's discuss how an FHA 203k loan can turn this property into the masterpiece you've been waiting for!
